      __________________________________________________________________

      Visit Kalamazoo Public Library's AV department on the lower level of
      our beautiful downtown building, or give us a call at (616) 553-7802...
      AV staff are available during all open hours.

      For loan period information, new holdings at our downtown location, new
      services being offered (including CD-ROM, DVD, and MP3 player loans),
      and helpful links to other websites, click any of the links below:

