                       THIS MONTH'S FEATURED DISPLAYS

   Adults... let it snow and let the cold wind blow!  Dim the lights, curl
   up with some hot cocoa, and let classic tales of romance pluck at your
   heartstrings!  Kids... so you loved the Harry Potter books and you've
   seen the first Lord of the Rings movie... what's next?  Check out our
   suggestions for other authors who write in the fantasy fiction genre.
   Videos and audiobooks for kids and adults alike are available NOW...
   stop by our AV department and see these displays today!

